Comment: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:13.90,ED2,,0,0,0,,ROCKET THRUSTER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.80,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você se sente sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:13.60,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você consegue me ouvir agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:19.14,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Sua mente está tão longe, ainda na Terra
